<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10012575>
    dc:description "FIGURE 8. Prothyma (Symplecthyma) heteromallicollis Horn, 1909. a) Dorsal habitus, Holotype, male. b) Elytra, female. Scale = 5 mm. c) Head and labrum, male; d) Head and labrum, female. Scale = 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10012575/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10012579>
    dc:description "FIGURE 9. Aedeagus of Prothyma (Symplecthyma) heteromallicollis Horn, 1909. a–b) Holotype; c–e) Luzon, Cagayan, St. Ana; f) Mindanao, Luagon; g–h) Mindanao, Nabunturan; i–j) Mindanao, Davao de Oro. Scale = 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10012579/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

